Type: Package
Package: fingR
Title: A package to support sediment source fingerprinting studies 
Version: 2.0.0
Authors:
  person("Thomas", "Chalaux-Clergue", role = c("aut","cre","cph"), email = "thomaschalaux@icloud.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-3525-832X")),
  person("Rémi", "Bizeul", role = c("aut", "cph"), email = "rbizeul59@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4103-9839"))
Maintainer:
  The package maintainer <thomaschalaux@icloud.com> and <rbizeul59@gmail.com>
Description:
  A package to support sediment source fingerprinting studies:
  characterising your dataset, selecting tracers (three-step method, range test conservativity test, discriminant power (Kruskal-Wallis H-test, Kolmogorov-Smirnov two-samples test)),
  modelling source contribution (BMM with or without stable isotopes) and assessing the quality of modelling predictions using virtual mixtures (support BMM and MixSIAR).
